      <title>中国汽车制造商在欧盟新一轮听证会上反击关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/chinese-carmakers-push-back-against-tariffs-in-new-eu-hearings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在北京和布鲁塞尔继续在 11 月确定关税的最后期限之前进行谈判之际，被欧盟反补贴调查中点名的三家中国汽车制造商已寻求并获得了欧盟监管机构的额外听证会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/chinese-carmakers-push-back-against-tariffs-in-new-eu-hearings</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 05:22:00 GMT</pubDate>
